    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It has been super well-maintained and still runs like a total dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable, stylish car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and is just waiting for someone new to take it on its next big adventure. You\u2019re going to love how it handles on the road! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
