      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Alpine White. This example features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear 8,000 RPM powerband. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise engagement, complemented by a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing replacement. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis maintains its legendary 50/50 weight distribution. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain is optimized for peak performance and high-G cornering.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Routine maintenance performed.",
      "price": 31500.0,
