    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and very well-loved. Whether you're zipping through your daily commute or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is totally ready for its next adventure. It runs like a charm and looks great too! I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 32500.0,
