      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six powerplant and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and documented VANOS overhaul, ensuring structural and mechanical integrity under high-load cornering. The M-Variable differential provides exceptional torque distribution across the rear axle, while the individual throttle bodies offer instantaneous throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Suspension geometry remains tight with recent bushing refreshes. While showing light cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust, delivering the visceral, analog feedback sought by purists.",
